Recent Builds and Checks

Source: R/runiv_stats_checks.R
runiv_stats_checks.Rd

Get list with recent builds and checks of packages available in an R-universe.

runiv_stats_checks(universe)

Arguments

universe

A length one character. User or organization name of the the R-universe owner.

Value

a data.frame.

Author

Valerio Gherardi

Examples

runiv_stats_checks("vgherard")
